Term data for 98,000 undergraduates

Source: R/midfieldterms.R
midfieldterms.Rd

Data frame of term attributes of 97,064 undergraduates with 727,369 observations and 13 academic term variables keyed by student ID and term. Each observation is one term for one student. A stratified sample of the MIDFIELD database.

midfieldterms

Format

data.table with 729,014 observations and 13 variables, occupying 82.1 MB of memory. Each observation is one term for one student. The variables are:

id

character, unique anonymized MIDFIELD student identifier

institution

character, anonymized institution name

cip6

character, 6-digit CIP code of instructional program during the term

term_course

numeric, academic year and term, format YYYYT

level

character, level

standing

character, standing

coop

character, coop "Y" or "N"

hours_term_attempt

numeric, credit hours attempted in the term

hours_term

numeric, credit hours earned in the term

gpa_term

numeric, term grade point average

hours_cumul_attempt

numeric, cumulative credit hours attempted

hours_cumul

numeric, cumulative credit hours earned

gpa_cumul

numeric, cumulative grade point average

Source

Data provided by the MIDFIELD project: https://engineering.purdue.edu/MIDFIELD

midfieldterms
